---
import { Network, Zap, Award, Gauge, Clock, Shield } from 'lucide-astro';

---
<section class="bg-[#F8FAFC] py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center mb-16"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#78BE20]/10 border border-[#78BE20]/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-full animate-pulse"></span><p class="text-[#78BE20] text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em]">Por qué elegirnos</p></div><h2 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">Beneficios</h2><div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] mx-auto mt-6 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1"><div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-b-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="mb-5"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#78BE20]/10 transition-colors duration-500"><Network class="lucide lucide-network w-7 h-7 text-[#0F2E65] group-hover:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-500" /></div></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Operadoras Tier 1</h3></div><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Conexión directa con las redes globales de mayor prestigio, garantizando una latencia mínima y una estabilidad superior en todas tus comunicaciones.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1"><div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-b-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="mb-5"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#78BE20]/10 transition-colors duration-500"><Zap class="lucide lucide-zap w-7 h-7 text-[#0F2E65] group-hover:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-500" /></div></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Rápida Implementación</h3></div><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Nuestro equipo especializado asegura una puesta en marcha ágil y sin complicaciones, para que tu operación esté lista en tiempo récord.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1"><div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-b-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="mb-5"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#78BE20]/10 transition-colors duration-500"><Award class="lucide lucide-award w-7 h-7 text-[#0F2E65] group-hover:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-500" /></div></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Pioneros de la Industria</h3><span class="bg-[#78BE20] text-[#0F2E65] text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">25 años</span></div><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Más de dos décadas de experiencia liderando el sector nos respaldan, ofreciendo soluciones probadas que evolucionan con las necesidades del mercado.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1"><div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-b-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="mb-5"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#78BE20]/10 transition-colors duration-500"><Gauge class="lucide lucide-gauge w-7 h-7 text-[#0F2E65] group-hover:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-500" /></div></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Velocidad Garantizada</h3></div><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Disfruta de un ancho de banda constante y optimizado. Nos comprometemos a mantener el rendimiento máximo que tu empresa necesita para ser competitiva.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1"><div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-b-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="mb-5"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#78BE20]/10 transition-colors duration-500"><Clock class="lucide lucide-clock w-7 h-7 text-[#0F2E65] group-hover:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-500" /></div></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Disponibilidad 24/7/365</h3></div><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Monitorización constante y soporte técnico especializado siempre activo. Estamos aquí para asegurar que tu servicio nunca se detenga.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1"><div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-b-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="mb-5"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#78BE20]/10 transition-colors duration-500"><Shield class="lucide lucide-shield w-7 h-7 text-[#0F2E65] group-hover:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-500" /></div></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Seguridad Empresarial</h3></div><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Protección robusta y protocolos de seguridad avanzada para blindar tu información crítica contra cualquier amenaza digital externa.</p></div></div></div></section>
